    <briefdescription>
<para>A container widget that enforces the aspect ratio of a child widget. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Using a provided width and height, this widget calculates the aspect ratio and forces the child widget to stay confined to that aspect ratio and centered within the widget.</para>
<para>The aspect ratio is calculated width divided by height. If the aspect ratio is zero (either width or height == 0), the widget is hidden until a valid size is provided. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
